The '''Society for the Scientific Study of Religion''' (founded in 1949)<ref>Glock, 2000 p. 243</ref> was formed to advance research in the social scientific perspective on religious institutions and experiences.<ref>[http://www.sssrweb.org/About.cfm SSSRweb.org: About Us]</ref>
==Journal for the Scientific Study of Religion==
The ''[[Journal for the Scientific Study of Religion]]'' is published by the Society to provide a forum for empirical papers in the topic area.
